<title>ạ̉nạ hạmlạ ạlkwn trnym</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr - ạ̉nạ hạmlạ ạlkwn trnym wạ̉gẖạny lrb ʿẓym
 ḥrrny fy ywm wfdạny wsẖrạny bdm krym
 1- rạḥ ạ̉ʿly ạlṣwt bhtạf wfy wạdy ạlmwt msẖ ạ̉kẖạf
 mlyạn bạ̉mạn mṭmn wmʿạyạ rạʿy ạlkẖrạf
 2- wrạḥ ạ̉ʿln bạltsbyḥ ạ̹ny mlk ạlmsyḥ
 hạrfʿ trnymy dẖbyḥẗ ḥmd wsẖkr wmdyḥ
 3- ṣwty hạywṣl llnạs yʿln ạ̉jml ạ̹ḥsạs
 frḥạn byswʿ mḥbwby ạlly whbny ạlkẖlạṣ</lyrics>
